// After creating this, in VS Code click the environment name in the bottom-right status bar 
// (or Ctrl+Shift+P → "Rest Client: Switch Environment") and pick dev — that's what makes {{baseUrl}} etc. resolve.


### Create Address (logged-in user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "addressLine1": "123 Main Street",
  "city": "Chennai",
  "state": "Tamil Nadu",
  "pincode": "600001",
  "isDefault": true
}

### Get My Addresses
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Update Address
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/addresses/{{addressId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "city": "Coimbatore"
}

### Delete Address
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/addresses/{{addressId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}